This plan shifts focus away from the CGM simulator (which your teammate will handle) and focuses entirely on making the Recommendation Engine the true "soul" of GlucoNav. We will migrate to real datasets, add Type 1 dosage predictions, support meal imagery, and fix the "sticky mock data" bug in the Flutter app.

